description: 1959 Ford Galxie Skyliner (Hard Top Convertible). In Great shape, orignal motor totally rebuilt, and original transmission. The engine is a 332 special V-8. Was professionally appraised by Gary Essay for $35,000. New radiator, battery, belts, hoses, and installed custom exhaust. Engine painted to orignal color. New brakes and new tires. All new parts original replicas! Continental package was added prior to me owning it. Body is in great shape! Have all documentation and receipts for motor rebuild and other work done including parts and labor. I have owned it for almost 5 years and it needs to be owned by someone that will do it justice. Get it to car shows to show it off!
